        titulo: "The Profile of a Controller",
        texto: "Beloved ones! There is no possibility of two souls existing with the same consciousness, with the same frequency and that could be said in the same condition within the evolutionary ladder. However, there are many that are similar or that act more or less in the same way; that have much similarity in their degree of understanding and that resemble each other by affinities, by actions and by reactions. In this way, placing them in similar groups, it becomes easier to also understand the individual process of each one. Whenever we say that others are our mirrors, we are wanting to show that, through comparisons, learning becomes easier. By observing the actions of those around us, when one is aware that we are in a school of souls, observing without emphasizing judgment, then lessons are absorbed more easily and more quickly. Earth as a School of Souls offers all learning opportunities within what can be called duality or polarities. The entire path is not the same and not in the same time for all students of this School. However, the one who reaches the end of the journey deserves approval for a School of a higher level. We call this fact Ascension. Humanity is now experiencing a unique moment within this long evolutionary journey. With the arrival of the new energies that promote the Planetary Transition, the greater infusion of Gamma Light begins to dissolve the veils of forgetfulness, and the incarnated souls who are about to ascend will gradually remember who they are, where they came from and why they were here. They will also remember the details of all past lives and all the learning conquered. The human beings incarnated here on Earth now who are ready for ascension, with each passing day, perceive how fast the changes are. They themselves can understand things that were not possible to understand before. The feeling is so heightened that they can actually evaluate each feeling of the one who is nearby or who comes into tune, even at a distance. They can feel even the intentions of the other, even if the other does not demonstrate. We are very close to reaching full Fifth Dimension consciousness. And at this level there will be no more deceptions and no manipulations. This will be the ruler that will determine who is indeed ready for the New Earth, which will also cease to be a World of Expiations and Trials to transform into a World of Regeneration. Currently, we can say that each human being is apt to understand certain situations and can make evaluations according to the real state of their consciousness. Therefore, it is necessary to be careful not to judge, for judgment is always made according to the internal vibrations and understanding of the one who judges. To judge is not to show the truth of the other, but your own exposed truth. When therapeutic work is done, the therapist is in the condition of assisting the one who seeks them. It is the exact moment when frequencies align, both of the one who receives and the one who gives the guidance. And today's text also serves as a therapeutic function. Not to judge people, but to guide them, for many will have the opportunity to understand those around them, and especially if any of you fits the condition of CONTROLLER or even MANIPULATOR. The controller is not an evil soul. It is indeed a soul that has not yet fully finalized learning. Therefore, it understands that others should be exactly like them. They should think, act, execute tasks according to their methodology. They do not accept that someone says something contrary to their beliefs, or that someone contradicts what they say. The Controller has in their unconscious a strong desire to be in command of all actions that involve something or someone that is nearby or that is known to them. It does not matter if the other does it better, it only matters that the other does it the way they would do it. The controller also possesses some edges still to be smoothed. Certainly among them are envy, pride, vanity, intolerance, anger, among others. But there is also still a lot of pain within their memories of past lives. So, the fear of going through pain again makes them demand to always be in control. Unconsciously, they believe that by being in control of everything, nothing will happen that could cause them the pains of the past. The controller generally possesses a charitable soul. The pains of past lives have already polished their soul to such an extent that now they only fear going through the same situations again. This is the reason that makes the controller have the permanent need for validation of their attitudes. That is why they demand so much from others. But deep down they are actually desirous of compliments. The controller is thirsty for these compliments, for the compliment is the way to prove that they are always right. On the other hand, if they receive criticism, it will drive them crazy. This happens because they still blame themselves for their past mistakes that caused them so much pain. Each criticism they receive revives in their subconscious the memories of the hard situations lived in the past. The controller is very bipolar, for they quickly alternate a loving attitude with an angry one. It is not easy to live with them. Many people distance themselves from them for this reason, which leads them to suffer greatly, even if they do not admit it in these cases. As consolation, they try to believe that the one who distanced themselves did not deserve to be in their company. But it is a solitary pain and wounds them mortally every time this happens. Few can actually live with them for a long time. However, as we always say: there are no victims, for the one who calls themselves a victim today was in fact the executioner of yesterday. So, living with the controller is indeed a learning still necessary for such people involved with them. And to leave no doubt, we leave here the observation that the controller is not properly a MANIPULATOR. If the controller is generally a charitable soul, the manipulator in essence is a soul that still needs much learning. Therefore, the manipulator is a person who still takes pleasure in evil and in the subjugation of other incarnated beings. This one is still far from the ascension of their soul. The manipulator takes pleasure in the pain of others. They possess few predicates, but have many flaws in their character, for they are generally proud, greedy, biased, ambitious, etc., but they are aware that they are a failure. So they try to compensate for their failure by imposing themselves on everything and everyone, for they do not tolerate someone being in superior conditions to them. The manipulator is a contumacious unhappy person. They compensate for their unhappiness by causing pain to others. The manipulator needs applause, for it is the only way to feel competent. Their permanent desire for power is also the great wound that mistreats them for a lifetime, for it is a wound that never heals. No matter how much power they achieve, it will never be enough to make them happy. It is a thirst that never ends! Deep down, they consider themselves the most unhappy among humans. Namaste!",
