        titulo: "The Importance of Conscious Breathing",
        texto: "Beloved ones! The more we understand the beauty and perfection of Divine Creation, the more amazed we become. Even though forces contrary to the Light have strived to impose limiting beliefs on human consciousnesses, nothing can prevent part of humanity from making its ascension now. In the countless previous texts that report on the Planetary Transition and the Ascension of Souls, we left numerous messages on the subject. The awakened consciousnesses begin to broaden very quickly. This brings a different understanding of the reality lived until now. It also brings all the unconscious knowledge that accompanies this soul fractal that is incarnated in human form. Yes, we are indeed at the end of a Great Planetary Cycle! A New Time is approaching, providing the Planetary Transition and our beautiful Blue Planet will no longer be even a shadow of what it was before. New Earth and New Humanity! All souls that incarnated in human form on this Planet collaborated in a certain way for its construction. Many will inherit it for also having achieved their Ascension. And even those who will have to leave it gave, in a certain way, a portion of themselves in this grandiose divine project. New times are approaching and changes are necessary and, at the same time, inevitable. But one should not expect changes from outside to inside. If you contributed to the construction of the New Earth, it was always with something that you already possessed within yourself. So it is also certain that the finishing of this work of art will also have to come by inspiration, that is, from within. You are the architect of the New Earth. Never forget that! But, above all, you are the architect of yourself. You transformed yourself into what you are today, through the construction and execution of each thought, act, or work, through all the hundreds of incarnations here on this Planet. Through the experiences lived, you molded your current consciousness. And it will be this consciousness that will determine the frequency that will enable the ascension or not of each one's soul. But, before ascension, we still need to go through the last lessons and the last learnings in order to obtain the key that will open the Fifth Dimension Portal. They are small details that will not bring great difficulties, at least for those who have already awakened. Always remembering that, for these, the worst is over. Awakening brings the understanding and the most comprehensive comprehension of each thing or situation. The more the consciousness of the awakened expands, the greater is the understanding of the process being lived today on Planet Earth. And the more consciousnesses broaden, the greater is the vibration and the higher becomes the frequency of the entire Planet. We begin to better understand that we are all ONE with the Source. We are all ONE with nature. We are all ONE as humanity and with the life existing in this planetary home. We begin to understand that we are much more supported than could be imagined. And, thus, we begin to transform ourselves into the New Human of the New Earth. The transition does not happen from one moment to another, we have said this so many times. But now, at its end, everything accelerates. Even so, we have the current existence to complete or give the finishing touch to our own architecture. And each one will give their personal and non-transferable touch to their work. What a precious moment this is! Wise is the one who knows how to take advantage of it! But today the text has the purpose of bringing to all of you who read it, a bit of information that the new consciousnesses can already absorb. Let us talk about THE POWER OF CONSCIOUS BREATHING. Breathing is a natural mechanism that keeps beings alive on this Planet. But let us talk only about human beings. Even spontaneously, everyone breathes, for if they do not, they obviously die. But, as it is natural, they do it unconsciously. And this is the great difference that we will address in today's text. Breathing consciously is different. Understanding its power and its benefits is only possible as each one's consciousness expands. Then, we begin to understand why breathing is called THE BREATH OF LIFE. Life would not exist if there were no Light. And the planetary Sun brings this Light that comes from the Central Sun, that is, from the Source. And the Source is where everything is created, and from it everything is sown throughout the infinite Universes. This Light is called PRANA. The pranas are in the solar spectrum, which can be proven through the rainbow. Pranas are seeds of life. They are, at the same time, the maintainers of this life in all corners of the Galaxies. Without Light there would be no pranas. And to keep the pranas active at night, they mix with water and air. That is why living beings do not die when the Sun sets. Having seen this, it is not only oxygen that we need, but also the pranas. So, we need to become aware of this composition of the air and know how to take advantage of it. There are interesting techniques in the practice of breathing. I can mention here an important source about this, which are the techniques called Pranayama Breathing. Research and see how fantastic it is. But you can practice and improve through intuition as well. Remember that your consciousness begins to bring the innate knowledge that is already within you. Practice will take you deeper and deeper into this knowledge. But, to begin such practices, I leave a little guidance here today. Whenever you feel fear, anxiety, anger, desperation, or any other emotional symptom, stop for 10 minutes everything you are doing and breathe consciously. Sit comfortably and close your eyes. Begin to pay attention to your breathing. Feel the air entering your body. Inhale through the nose slowly and deeply, to the point you can manage. Take this air intentionally beyond the lungs, make it reach the abdomen. Then release through the mouth, a little faster than the inhalation. At first, you may not achieve total concentration on breathing, but over time, everything will improve. The results will be felt more and more intensely. This conscious exchange of air promotes the exchange of energies as well. This is because you are in command and you direct the pranas. Pranas are pure energies and, upon reaching the cells of the body, they cleanse the impure energies that cause the unpleasant symptoms mentioned here before. In case you feel pain or physical discomfort in any part of the body, you can also do the same procedure. Breathe as in the previous technique and, when your lungs are full of air, send these pranas through the blood arteries and veins to the point where the pain is. Mentally irrigate this point with the pranas and then exhale the pain out. With practice, you will feel relief whenever you do this and, over time, you will learn to heal yourself from most pains. All healing techniques are valid; however, the result is not always the same for everyone who practices them. It depends on the understanding and consciousness of each one. It also depends on confidence and persistence. But the energies that the pranas bring are always pure and come from the Creative Source of everything there is. It is divine providence offering the support that is never lacking. No one is prevented from using such resources, for they are natural, free, and exist in abundance. Enjoy! Namaste!",
