        titulo: "The Ego Is an Existential Void",
        texto: "Beloved ones! The closer we get to the end of this Third Dimension Cycle, the more understanding we have of who we are and what we are. This is good, for it frees consciousnesses as they awaken and rise. The Divine Plan is fulfilled within all the Universal rules that govern each Planet and each Star. Humanity is now taking its last steps within that space that still corresponds to the frequencies of Worlds of Trials and Expiations. As each incarnated soul begins the crossing of the interdimensional bridge, all the knowledge accumulated through hundreds of incarnations on this Planet begins to be remembered. It is impressive how this is all very fast! As we have said here other times, what was yesterday, today is no longer. It can also be noted that in previous incarnations, everything that was planted in one existence was harvested in the following existence. Now it is different, for everything will be harvested immediately, that is, still within the current existence. The revelations will bring the entire history of humanity, both of individual consciousnesses and of the collective. A sample of this are the increasingly lucid dreams and also the countless sensations and symptoms that each one is currently feeling. All the fears accumulated in this current existence and also in previous ones will now manifest in order to be dissolved. The same will happen with anger, guilt, hurt, resentments, and all the negative emotions that each human being went through over the millennia. The decisive moment is now. If in the years 2019, 2020, and 2021 the healing was restricted to the ancestry corresponding to past lives, now in this year, especially in this second semester, the healing is being done in what corresponds to the past within this current life. This is the reason for so many symptoms currently. Pay attention to your dreams and see that they have a close relationship with something you went through in this current existence. This is the energetic cleansing that we must go through in order to adjust to higher frequencies. If this were not done, no one would be able to withstand the flashes of Photonic Light that reach Earth, each day with more power. We are also going through a necessary physical cleansing, since our DNA is being updated. It has already been said that the new human DNA will soon have 12 activated helices, whereas until now only two were active. This update is only possible as the physical bodies manage to detoxify from the chemical products accumulated in their organs and cells. But there are an infinity of necessary changes and each one faces their own demands. Each one has their individual history. And it is in their beliefs and emotions that the work is being done more deeply. It is the famous cleaning of their basements. As Light enters these basements, all the dirt becomes exposed. Thus, it facilitates the necessary work to dissolve such energies and such shadows. Today's theme brings a part referring to the soul baggage that still needs to be sorted and left behind. Unnecessary and useless, it should not be taken beyond the bridge mentioned at the beginning of the text. Let us talk about the EGO. The inflated ego, that is, an emotion, a belief, or even a need that many believe to be beneficial, but that when overdosed is tremendously harmful to the evolution of the soul. The ego is an empty space that needs to be filled. Not by egoic attitudes, but by something altruistic, by something that elevates the soul. The uncontrolled Ego is a treacherous guide that digs the abyss where it throws its follower. The ego builds nothing, only destroys the little that its bearer achieves with great difficulty. In truth, the ego is a certificate of incompetence. When one says inflated ego, we could understand that it is nothing more than an empty bubble, like a balloon full of air. The more it grows, the closer its collapse is, for, when it bursts, nothing useful will remain. Many feel a very great existential void within themselves, compared to an intense hunger. They urgently need to fill that space in order to free themselves from the discomfort of such emptiness. So they create an illusion in order to satisfy such a lack. This illusion is the ego that grows in proportion to the existing space. However, as the days pass, its bearer realizes that all attempts were fruitless. Just like a balloon that deflates over time, that space filled with the ego also dissolves and the need for more ego arises. The more the ego broadens, the greater the space occupied and more and more need arises. This becomes an endless vicious cycle. The ego produces nothing useful. This is the reason it never satisfies the one who holds it. It is just a deceptive appearance camouflaged in the mind of its bearer. It does not even fool anyone, whether the one who is nearby or even a stranger. The inflated ego does not even hide a despicable attitude of the one who carries it, for, as it is something that grows, it ends up showing itself more easily to everyone. The ego also reveals something that no one likes to show: the difference between a winner and a loser. It only identifies, among so many, the least apt for great works. Yes, for the one who actually accomplishes something good does not need this artifice, for they already feel fulfilled all the time. This one does not feel the existential void that the egoic one feels. The one who is competent does not need to prove anything, for their accomplishments speak for themselves. The bearer of the inflated ego tries to show something they cannot have or accomplish. The ego is a void that needs to be filled; not with illusion, but with uplifting things. So, the ego is something that still needs to be understood. Namaste!",
