        titulo: "Value or Price?",
        texto: "Beloved ones! The time of revelations has arrived. Nothing more will remain hidden, neither before the eyes nor before consciousnesses. We are in the last phase of the Transition, exactly the one that precedes the greater Event, the one that will break the threads that still connect us to the Third Dimension World. All Systems known to humanity will undergo a reset so that the reinitializations of the New Systems can be activated. The expectation of the incarnated soul is great now. Even though human consciousness still cannot comprehend the grandeur of such events, the soul in its highest version clearly glimpses what is to come. With each passing day, more and more consciousnesses previously wrapped in the veils of forgetfulness begin to expand their understanding, allowing each incarnated being to have the opportunity to awaken from the long dark night of illusion. What you did not understand a year ago now seems so familiar! Subjects you were not interested in before now begin to make sense. What seemed fiction before now seems to be indeed an acceptable reality. And everything that seemed real begins to show itself illusory. Yes, you are waking up! The high frequency energy that arrives on Earth now provokes such opportunities. All the awakenable ones will now have a propitious time to open their eyes definitively. There will be no more illusions for this portion of humanity. We have said so many times that the Planetary Transition is in its final moments. At least one third of the incarnated will be able to ascend in this current incarnation. Remembering also that this is the last opportunity, since there will be no other incarnation in duality here on Planet Earth. There was enough time for all souls to prepare. Hundreds and even more than a thousand previous incarnations, most of the incarnated have already had. No one will be able to say that they did not have time to learn what duality means. Everyone went through the possible and imaginable polarities offered by this School of Souls. Time runs out quickly now! What took Centuries before can now take only a few months. Time is urgent for all of us! Wake up! Do not sleep now! See the text from last week, October 12 of this year 2022. The hour is already late and many will not realize that time is also running out. The Portals of ascension are already open. It is necessary to pass through them in order to reach the New Earth. When the gong sounds, they will close for the latecomers and nothing more can be done for their benefit. There was no lack of messages or messengers bringing the Good News. There was no lack of opportunities to redeem oneself from bad actions. There were no lack of signs coming from all sides and from Above. But it was always said that there would have to be ears to hear and eyes to see. Understanding the objective of each one being here incarnated on Earth. Everyone was warned! Insistently warned! Now the separation of the chaff from the wheat is finalized. NOW EVERYONE WILL KNOW THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN VALUE AND PRICE. Value and price are quite different things. Many incarnated gave more importance to ethical and moral values and to qualities conquered through hard trials. While others merchandised through the price of each act or action. A man who has value has conquered riches in Heaven. The one who determined a price for each act or action conquered goods that will cease to exist, for they are ephemeral. They will be worth nothing to him now. On the contrary, what had a price will have to be redeemed, since all debts must be paid. Many prefer to sell themselves in order to obtain worldly advantages. These have a price. Others prefer to build a life based on the righteousness of each act, always respecting everything and everyone, living their days in their most perfect conscience of ethics and responsibility. These are humans who have value. Value can serve as currency in exchange when crossing the Portals of Ascension. The price is the quota to be paid before crossing the Portals. So now you begin to better understand such differences. The price is the amount to be paid, and this has no other possibility. Value is what is really worth, and there is no money in the world that can pay for it. Many incarnated allow themselves to be bought and for this they set a price. They spend such accumulated resources on worldly things, for what is easily gained is also easily consumed. Like merchandise, they are traded. Remembering here the parable of the Merchants of the Temple. These will not inherit the Kingdom of Heaven, that is, they will not go through the ascension that will lead to the New Earth. Those who honored moral values earned the merit to inherit the New Earth. And this is priceless! There is nothing in the world that can buy such a precious good of such value. Do not create fortunes on Earth to the detriment of the riches of Heaven. This message alone summarizes everything that is written in today's text. Many allow themselves to be sold for any trinket. In these times of elections, we see how there are still people who have a price. Interests are sold or bought by those who have no value. They merchandise in the Sacred Temple their soul. They serve the interests of a few to the detriment of many. Have you already calculated how many sell themselves for R$ 100.00? They are the ones who do not value themselves. They sell themselves for so little! Even those who sell themselves for millions. Little do they know that it will be the price they will have to pay, multiplied by all the harm they caused to other people, for the redemption will require the price added to all the suffering caused through such a greedy gesture. Perhaps it is time for each one to evaluate their moment. Do you have value or just a price? Namaste!",
