        titulo: "The Light Is Within You",
        texto: "Beloved ones! The souls incarnated on this Third Dimension Planet have forgotten who they are, where they came from and what they came here to do. This is the rule in this School, for the learning is exactly this: to create something while the soul is subjected to the veil of forgetfulness. All souls came from the Light. Even those who before were in other worlds also of Trials and Expiations, long before were in Dimensions of 5D and above. Remembering that only a Fractal of an elevated soul can descend to Third Dimension worlds, for the risk of remaining in this low frequency range is very great. From the Light we came and to the Light we will return one day. Each one in due time, for there are no limited deadlines. What happens is that 3D Schools also make their Transition and, when that happens, souls need to migrate to other Schools still of the same level. So the exile of souls occurs, like those of Chapel who arrived here in times past. Now Earth is also making its Transition to 5D and will cease to be a World of Expiations and Trials. Upon passing to a World of Regeneration, the souls that achieved the highest frequency rise along with the New Earth. On the other hand, those not yet ready must leave it and face exile. The souls that are getting ready for ascension feel the changes in an increasingly intense way. They feel that something great is coming and they also feel an incredible need to transform themselves. Something very strong drives such souls to seek more knowledge and reasons for internal transformation. It is a thirst for knowledge that seems insatiable. Along with it also come uncertainties and anguish. Although the soul has much unconscious knowledge, consciousness still has all the experiences lived in this current incarnation. It also has the memories and records of the experiences of past existences in physicality. They are beliefs that still remain alive within each incarnated soul. Instinct is natural in every being. Like a compass that guides the walk, it often confuses, for it can indicate several directions at the same time. It is the influence of the mind addicted to what has already been experienced and lived throughout the successive incarnations of the soul. Timelines can overlap and create a tangle of situations and options. Everything needs to be resolved in this current incarnation. We came now to find the Line that leads to the 5D Portal. These are exciting and decisive times as well. Something great is coming and the soul knows it. Since we do not remember the divine project nor our own soul plan, it is natural that most incarnated now feel a great expectation, often transformed into deep anxiety. At certain moments, such anxiety can even turn into an unpleasant anguish. This is also one of the reasons for the increase in suicides. Others may feel a lot of anger, disillusionment, sadness, which can lead to deep depression or even madness. Therefore, we need to understand the current moment of humanity and the Planetary Transition. If this is the long-awaited moment since we accepted to come here to experience duality, why are we so distressed? If the best is yet to come, where is our confidence in the Divine Plan? If we have made it this far and the worst is over, why so much fear? The answers can be many, but the truth is only one. We are in the last hour of the night and darkness still prevents us from seeing the Light, but it will soon appear radiant like a new dawn. We still have the veils of forgetfulness wrapped around our consciousness; however, soon, one by one, all will be lifted quickly. It will then be the moment when we can remember who we really are. But until then, and this will not take as long as many believe, we still need to grope here and there in search of this long-awaited Light. Many still search for it disorderly. They keep going around and around, for they do not know which direction to follow. But the secret begins to be unveiled. And gradually, everyone will realize that THE LIGHT IS WITHIN EACH ONE. Do not seek anything outside of you! Just seek some parameters in order to locate yourself, for you carry all the necessary baggage for ascension. You have accumulated all the necessary experience in order to achieve the frequency of the New Earth. Search within this soul baggage and all the tools will be there. THE LIGHT IS THERE WAITING FOR YOU TO FIND IT. The Light is within you, for it has always been there. You never lost it! You just forgot that you always carried it with you. You came with it and with it you will return home. You just experienced the shadow while you forgot that you were always Light. You came to experience what it is like to create in a 3D world. You discovered that Light creates much more in Shadow than within the Light itself. YOU ARE THE LIGHT! YOU HAVE ALWAYS BEEN LIGHT AND WILL NEVER CEASE TO BE. Do not let yourself be involved by those who take pleasure in non-Light. Find reasons to feel the Light that you are. Do not allow the dark news to envelop you. Do not disseminate or share messages that hide the Light. Those of non-Light only have this tool left to maintain their survival on this Planet. Do not prolong their stay here. Do not feed such entities with low energy. You are Light, you just need to convince yourself of it! You do not depend on anything outside to achieve your ascension. Trust the Plan. AND TRUST THE LIGHT THAT IS WITHIN YOU! Namaste!",
        nivel: "advanced"
