        titulo: "Where Do Simple and Ignorant Spirits Come From?",
        texto: "Beloved ones! When Kardec codified Spiritism, he brought comfort to incarnated souls, since humans began to understand that life continues, even with the death of the physical body. In a way, humanity received a thread of Light in their consciousnesses, for understanding that death does not exist for the soul was indeed a great achievement in terms of knowledge for each incarnated here on Earth. Even so, Kardec's Spiritist Doctrine was limited to the Wheel of Reincarnations. All those who were interested in studying it interpreted that each human being is a simple and ignorant Spirit in search of improvement and evolution. In a way, this is correct, serving as comfort to those who strive in this evolution. Once all the lessons of this school of souls are learned, the cycle of reincarnations ends. But there was always a doubt: WHERE DOES ALL THIS BEGIN AND WHERE DOES IT END? It took almost two Centuries for human consciousnesses to at least begin to understand what goes beyond Kardecism. Gradually, when one understands something more than such doctrine, an infinite range of information emerges, bringing more and more information about who we really are. First we discovered that we are not a Spirit, but a soul fragmented from the Spirit. We are a Monad, that is, an unlimited consciousness, created in the Divine Source, as a DIVINE SEED-ATOM. This is the true Spirit, our HIGHER SELF, made in the image and likeness of the Creator, for He Himself is a Consciousness, the Source itself, what can be called GOD. Who is God? De-EUs (Of-YOUs), that is, the sum of all the YOUs, which is in fact everything that exists in the infinite Cosmos. He is the tree that created all the seeds. We are all seeds. And to spread, populate and create worlds, each Seed-Atom divided into 12 Super Souls, then into 12 more still Super Souls. Subsequently, each Super Soul divided into Souls and these, in turn, into Fractals to be able to reach the lower worlds. Therefore, who is incarnated as a human being on Earth is a Fractal of soul, that is, a tiny part of each monadic consciousness. Some previous texts have already been written here, explaining what Monads are like. So, the fractal is the smallest part of a consciousness that can still return to its higher version, without completely losing its monadic connection. Even subjected to the veil of forgetfulness, it will ascend when it has all its experiences here on this Planet. It was said that being in a World of Duality, of Expiations and Trials, is the farthest point a consciousness can experience life. Today, we begin to understand that this is the point where reason still accompanies consciousness, even subjected to the veils, but it is not yet the farthest point from the Source where parts of consciousnesses have permission to go create, learn and evolve. We have also said here before that, at the end of learning, these experiences are integrated into our higher soul versions. And this is carried forward until it reaches our HIGHER SELF, which is indeed the individualized Spirit. Once such experiences arrive there, they are also integrated into the WHOLE, for each Spirit is part of the greater Consciousness, unique as Source, that is, the Creator Himself: God. (OF YOUs). Having seen this, the souls incarnated on Earth, even limited, are consciousnesses provided with reason. They are aware of their acts and can decide, through their free will, each decision to be made. It is these decisions that advance or delay their evolution, and also the time they must remain here, in order to complete their learning purpose. Because they have this consciousness and reason, we cannot classify such souls as Simple and Ignorant as we believed until now. Certainly other channelers have also received information from Above on the subject addressed here. However, I was instructed to post the subject today, in order to bring to you who do not yet have such information about it. The point is that the souls incarnated on Earth have already come as Fractals of higher versions; therefore, they cannot be simple or ignorant. They are only subjected to the veil of forgetfulness. God does not create worlds as we believed before. Those who create are His Seeds. Remember the phrase: Go and multiply; create and populate the worlds. So, wherever a small Fractal of each Higher Consciousness is, it will be bringing Light to every place. It is the Light that creates, even in its smallest particle. And if God is Light, the Source is Light, you are Light. You are and always will be part of the Divine Seed-Atom. So, if each soul incarnated on Earth is a part of this Light, it cannot be simple and ignorant as we understood. Today I was given another part of our own Monad that I did not even imagine existed: our even lower versions, which cannot even be considered fractals, for they are such a tiny part of our consciousness, that they are not even possessors of reason. This part of us is materialized in the form and condition of Kingdoms lower than the human, that is, in the mineral, vegetable and animal Kingdom. We already knew that such Kingdoms were also consciousnesses, even in a primitive and evolving form, but we did not have the information that they are parts of each Monad to which we also belong. Even being consciousness without reason, each animal, each vegetable and each mineral particle is a version of us that went to experience life in those conditions. Each consciousness of these Kingdoms one day evolves from mineral to vegetable; from vegetable to animal; and then from animal to human. Upon arriving in human form, it acquires the condition of soul, adding reason to consciousness, and it is at this stage that it passes to the condition that was called Simple and Ignorant Spirit, for this process is the reverse of the incarnated soul that descended directly from a higher Dimension. This soul coming from the Lower Kingdoms brings the experience that no soul coming from above can take to the Higher Self. Once taken to the Source, everyone can know and understand what such experience is like, for we are all ONE in this Source. When we study Genesis, we have a lot of information about the evolution of worlds, but there is always some complementation missing, which I believe can only come when we have the capacity to understand such complexities. Our current consciousness is rapidly broadening and this facilitates the understanding of what is coming. One of the reasons why many souls come from Higher Dimensions to experience life in a Third Dimension World is, undoubtedly, to bring support to these evolving souls, also called Simple and Ignorant Spirits. Glorious times these that we live now! With each passing day, more information arrives. Thus, we will quickly finalize the assembly of the great puzzle that is this incredible work of the Creator. Each of us is a piece of this game. Praises be given at all times, for the revelations are already visible on the horizon line. I am Vital Frosi and my mission is enlightenment. Namaste!",
